---
By: Peace Pilgrim
Locus:
  Page: 96
  Verse: 13
Tags:
  - Desire
---
It’s very important to get your desirescentered so you will desire only to
doGod’s will for you. You can come to a point of oneness of desire, just to
know and do your part in the Life Pattern. When you think about it, is
there anything else as really important to desire?
